Name: Green Faux Georgette Designer Gown with Sequined Dupatta – Fully Flared Elegant Ready-to-Wear Set

Step into elegance with this premium Faux Georgette gown-dupatta set, designed to combine traditional charm with modern style. Ideal for weddings, parties, festive occasions, and cultural events, this ready-to-wear designer set perfectly balances style, comfort, and sophistication.
